::DarkMouse:

She was starting to wake up.  She couldn't open her eyes yet, but she 
could hear noises.  It sounded like lazar fire.  She tried to move 
but couldn't.  Her body wouldn't obey her.  Her head was spinning or 
felt like it was.  All she could do was hear what was happeneing 
without being able to do anything.  Somewhere inside her, she found 
that very frustrating.
